name: Unidentified_Grysk_captain_(FateSpinner)
content:
A Grysk was the captain of the FateSpinner. During the last battle above Sunrise, fought between the Grysk Hegemony's forces and the Kilji Illumine and the Chiss Ascendancy, the Grysk temporarily commanded the FateSpinner, a Shatter-class WarMaster, Jixtus' flagship until Jixtus returned from the Whetstone and took command. During the time period in which the Grysk commanded the FateSpinner, the WarMaster stayed idle in the center of the battle until Jixtus began to lead the battle aboard the warship and made the massive warship attack other ships.
The FateSpinner's commander was mentioned in the 2021 novel Thrawn Ascendancy: Lesser Evil, the final volume in the Star Wars: The Ascendancy Trilogy written by Timothy Zahn.
